genresAdvancedInfo.name: trap cristiano
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Trap cristiano is a Spanish-language subgenre of trap music that also incorporates Christian themes and messages into its lyrics. It emerged in Latin America and has gained popularity among young Christians who enjoy listening to trap music but also want to connect with their faith. The genre often features auto-tuned vocals, catchy hooks, and trap beats, with lyrics that focus on faith, redemption, and spirituality.
